:

1. On je *priznao* da je pogrešio. (He admitted that he was wrong.)
2. Ona je *priznata* kao jedan od najboljih u svojoj oblasti. (She was acknowledged as one of the best in her field.)
3. *Priznajte* da ste se prevarili. (Admit that you have been deceived.)
4. On je *priznavao* svoju odgovornost. (He acknowledged his responsibility.)
5. *Priznajte* da je to istina. (Admit that it is true.)
6. Ona je *priznala* da je lažovala. (She admitted that she was lying.)